      "content": {
        "title": "Hand Fractures and Dislocations — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Fractures of metacarpals and phalanges and dislocations of MCP, PIP, and DIP joints including thumb CMC instability.",
        "summary": "Boxer's fracture of fifth metacarpal neck often managed closed. Bennett and Rolando fractures require thumb CMC stabilization. Gamekeeper's thumb needs UCL repair."
